results.overview: Sinterklaas wants to be absolutely sure that all the presents will be delivered on time. To make that happen, he has come up with a clever plan: a secret gift storage facility in the Netherlands! Months before the official arrival, he secretly goes to check how things are going. But when he arrives, he gets the shock of his life: there are no presents at all! The Piets have received false instructions, and the arrival ceremony has been mysteriously canceled. Someone is pretending to be Sinterklaas — but who…?
results.title: Sinterklaas: The Mystery Of The Presents

But the hero in him must emerge if he is to save the world from annihilation and become the symbol of hope for all mankind.

results.overview: Exploring the history of the 'Power Rangers' franchise, casting, special effects and music.
